2.1.0
	* Renamed Templavoila controller
	* Removed obsolete smarty functions
	* use composer to load Smarty
	* Use same template folders as Fluid
	* Fallback to Fluid, if no template was found

2.0.0
	* support for TYPO3 6.1
	* namespaces
	* fluid block tag

1.3.0
	* support for TYPO3 4.5 and 4.7 in one extension
	* automatic escaping of all strings

1.2.0
	* template render function will evaluate all typoscript entries in settings.typoscript
	* TemplaVoilaController extends Action Controller
	* move setup to ext_typoscript_setup.txt so it will be automatically included
	* Cache templates in typo3temp instead of within the extension
	* Hook into Clearcache in the backend to clear the cache

1.1.0
	* Added TemplaVoilaController

1.1.0
	* initial version